#

Braised Short Ribs with Red Wine Reduction

$35
800 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

BeefComfort FoodGourmetSlow-Cooked

Description

Tender, fall-off-the-bone beef short ribs slow-cooked in a rich red wine sauce that elevates the flavors to a gourmet experience.

Ingredients

  • Beef short ribs: 4 lbs
  • Red wine: 2 cups
  • Beef stock: 2 cups
  • Carrots: 2, diced
  • Onion: 1 large, chopped
  • Celery: 2 stalks, chopped
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Thyme: 2 sprigs
  • Rosemary: 1 sprig
  • Bay leaves: 2
  • Olive oil: 3 tbsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
